{
  "stem": "2533.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Looked and looked and looked, and of a sudden, I found Gomerski.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Even the secretary was clapping.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She was so happy for me that I found him, that I really was in Sobibor, that I didn't make it up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Later on, it came for Frenzel I had to, and for Bauer, because I did remember some of them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And after 1983, I didn't want to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They asked me, but I recline.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then I got letters from Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Schneeweiss, it's my duty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And-- and I said, I'm not going alone to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "My husband wasn't well already then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I can't go alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They said they will pay for Andrew so Andrew can bring me to Hagen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was I had to be there for the 17th of April.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When was Easter time?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "April or March?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "April.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I got to to Frankfurt, from Frankfurt to Hagen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the next day I went to Hagen court, and I walked into-- it was a big, big foyer in the court.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a man standing a little bit further than that wall or the other wall there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said to Judge Kramer, what is Frenzel doing there-- here?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He looked at me, wanted to introduce me to the translator, and there was-- it was a woman.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He said, how do you know that that's Frenzel?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I just recognize him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was standing there at the profile, the side, leaning on a cane.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had like not a raincoat, but all-weather coat on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I looked at him, the first glance and I recognized him after 40 years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was in civilian clothing, and all I knew him was in military uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
